articles.title: How Modi won back India’s big economic prize five months after losing it - Al Jazeera English
articles.description: The BJP’s record win in Maharashtra underscores how it has bounced back from its setback in parliamentary elections.
articles.content: New Delhi, India An alliance led by Prime Minister Narendra Modis Bharatiya Janata Party (BJP) swept elections to Indias second-largest state, Maharashtra, on Saturday, dramatically regaining ground … [+7604 chars]
